node.text:
Go to the link in our @moonomens bio to get your free Eclipse Season Horoscope e-book for your sign! 
🦕
Last month we were covering the start of Eclipse Season and sharing about this powerful event and what it was initiating in all of our lives. If you experienced pivotal life altering moments and felt overwhelming surges of emotions, you weren't alone.
⚡️
Eclipses are emotionally charged events because they can change your whole life in one blink of an eye sometimes, but they also come in waves and they happen as storylines, which means that there is always an ongoing process whether you’re aware of it or not. Eclipses are always felt long before they happen and long after they happen. Their influence can last up to six months and even longer. 

Zooming out..

This series of Eclipses in Gemini/Sagittarius started in June of 2020 and they will end in January of 2022. Having Eclipses in these signs mean that things will be focused around truth and lies, education, mind, mental processes, mental health, mental barriers, educational system, knowledge, learning, breaking out of ignorance and stepping into our personal truths, spreading our voice and truth, spreading information, learning to discern between truth and lies, between valuable and invaluable information. It is about finding our truth within ourselves, being our own spiritual teachers, finding our inner guru, trusting in ourselves, reaching our higher mind, going towards our highest selves through knowledge, wisdom, spiritual encounters, philosophy, books, legacy of ancestors, legacy of our own selves from the past. 
🔮
Given that we are in the middle of a powerful Eclipse season, we have created free eclipse season horoscopes for all twelve signs to help you all navigate the next six months and gain clarity on what's unfolding. Enjoy!
🦕 
Go to the link in our @moonomens bio to get your free Eclipse Season Horoscope e-book for your sign!
